@bearerToken = {{bearerToken}}

### 1. Create a new Hello
POST http://localhost:8080/hello
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "test"
}

### 2. Get all Hellos
GET http://localhost:8080/hello
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### 3. Search Hellos by message
GET http://localhost:8080/hello/findByMessage?message=test
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### 4. Delete Hello by ID (replace 1 with actual ID from create response)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/hello/6
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### 6. Create another Hello for testing
POST http://localhost:8080/hello
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Another test message"
}

### 7. Get all Hellos again
GET http://localhost:8080/hello
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}